Congratulations to the 1st Bluedragon (Blue Dragon/BSA) Series Awards 2022 recipient, Mr. Kim Jongin aka KAI, who was awarded the Best (Rookie) Male Entertainer Award, for his part in the Netflix reality series, "New World."

author: @withoutnoun.4074
text:
Hello, Kai. 
 Here I am again, I know, that you did not notice my absence or my presence, I will delude myself that you missed me among the thousand messages that you receive.
 We are only a few hours away from the ripening of the peaches, I am excited and my heart is pounding, so before it is uploaded, I wanted to tell you something you will not read, but write it so that I may get lucky this time with you, we Ex-Os are proud of you no matter what the result You have worked hard  And you exhausted yourself a lot, so please get some rest and don't overthink about the album, because it will be good in our eyes no matter what the outcome, not only because you are like from EXO, but because you are like the creator even in bad things 💙🍑.
مرحبا، كاي. 
ها قد عدت مجددا أعلم، انك لم تلاحظ غيابي أو وجودي، سأوهم نفسي أنك أفتقدتني بين الالف الرسائل التي تصلك. 
لم يعد يفصلنا عن نضوج الخوخ سوى بضع ساعات، أشعر بالحماس وقلبي يخفق بشدة، لذا قبل أن يتم تحميله، أردت أن أخبرك شيء ما أنت لن تقرأ، لكن أكتبه لعله حظي يحالفني هذا المره معك، نحن الاكسوالز فخورين بك مهما كانت النتيجه لقد عملت بجد وأرهقت نفسك كثيرا، لذا من فضلك نل قسطا من الراحه ولا تفرط في التفكير بشأن اللبوم، لانه سيكون جيد في نظرنا مهما كانت نتيجه، ليس لانك كاي من اكسو فقط، بل لانك كاي المبدع حتى في الاشياء السيئة 💙🍑.

author: @withoutnoun.4074
text:
Kai, you are a great warrior, you know when to fight your battles, get up and dust you off, ride your horse (today you'll shine) you're in the front line, everyone is watching, 💙🍑.  Everyone is proud of you for what you have done now and in the future.
- exo = exols ♡゙♡゙.

author: @conflictivot
text: Ni siquiera 1M. Recuerdo a algunos EXOL decir que se decepcionaron del concepto. Yo misma vi esos comentarios y ahora veo los comentarios en las plataformas de los antis burlandose de Jongin que a los EXOL no les gusto el concepto suave porque querian un concepto sexy de kai y con menos ropa bailando y que no les importa que cante, solo que mueva el cuerpo. Este fandom de mierda es tan decepcionante, ingrato y mentiroso y algunos vienen con la frase de mierda SOMOS UNO adonde cuando kai debuto ni alcanzo el millon de ventas y Do tampoco. Todos los seguidores de Exo para que sirven. Siento pena por kai que este fandom LAZY no valore realmente su trabajo como cantante y solo lo quiere verle mover el cuerpo y luego vienen algunos EXOL HIPOCRITAS a  insultarme  y decirme que soy resentida y que kai ama y es devoto del fandom , la embarro mas y pobre kai asi le pagan todo su trabajo y amor por este fandom ingrato. Extrano ese fandom de anos que era mas unido ya se perdio todo eso. Desde que Exo entro en pausa y los integrantes empezaron como solistas se fue todo al carajo y ellos mismos le pedian a SM que cada miembro debutara como solista y ahi seseparo el fandom, porque empezo la guerra de quien cantaba mejor, quien vendia mas y todas esas estupideces, cuando lo ideal que las ventas de albunes fueran parejas para todos porque todos queriamos ver debutar a nuestros miembros como solistas y triunfar en su debut con su album.  Solo el 1 % del fandom sigue leal a todos el resto pura ingratitud y POSER

author: @sholjas13
text: The strength of the Ballerina is still so obvious. Glad seeing the interpretive use of various effects, yet maybe less opportunity of distraction and more soloist focus on the dance interpretations could be an interesting future effort. Many decades now, a lot of kudos has been attributed to the technology side of music production. The synthesised effects are flowing into background effects, beyond the era when the mv had more importance than the tune. Younger artists especially appreciate opportunities where Production Teams collate many aspects of the finished product, yet the fans want to see the stars they love. Each song shouldn't be a showcase of technology beyond the artist's talent. Equipment is progressed. Talent evolves, and the fans want to be part of that evolution. They can admire the technology yet they engage with the stars they love. ❤👄☯️👾✌

author: @conflictivot
text: Que paso que siento un apoyo tan bajo en esto. Las vistas de los MV tan bajas, otros diciendo que estan decepcionados, que no les gusto el concepto y que esperaban a kai con poca ropa. Ahi si irias a full de streming para verlo una y otra vez. Acepto que no te guste porque creo en la libertad de expresion, asi como yo me he expresado aqui y digo lo que siento sin filtro. Pero cuando estan tirando negatividad ya es otra cosa.a los antis sin trabajo no me interesan lo que digan. Pero los del fandom que se dicen EXOL son tan ingratos con Jongin, cuando el ha sido tan comprometido, trabajando duro para darles contenido, dando su 100 % )para los fans, promocionando a EXO aqui y alla.realmente el fandom aparte de ser Lazy con todo EXO en apoyo son ingratos. El que se sienta identificado que le llegue este mensaje, nunca realmente apreciaran a Jongin y su gran talento como artista, siempre lo veran solo como el bailarin principal sexy que las hace felices mostrando piel, son tan decepcionantes una vez mas. Si no puedes decirle a Jongin nada positivo mejor callate y no le desees cosas malas , son una mierda Con un himbre cin un corazon tan amable, por la situacion que mas odio es cuando kai hace promocion al grupo o SM lo usan para promocionara otros idolis en sus videos , no merecen a kai y su trabajo duro, ojala pronto se vaya y haga su propia carrera cimo cantante o lo que quiera perofuera de esa maldita empresa y del grupo. Los otros mie bros no tienen la culpa, es el fandom que ya se separo definitivamente. Ingratos

author: @kristinangelicatubig6680
text: I started liking him for his visuals - handsome face, hot body, sexiness. I love him for his beautiful heart as a person. An artist who is much beloved from everyone that has worked with him. The one who cherishes his fans so much and always make us smile in every way possible. The one who always be kind and gentle and happy like a ball of sunshine. But what make me really stay as a fan even after years is his talent and passion. He always has that ‘wow factor’ that make me in awe and respect him. That talent that makes him stand out. And he even keeps growing and improving in all aspects. He’s always top-tier in dance, no doubt. But he also has beautiful voice and great taste in creating arts. He’s also growing as an entertainer who got people surprised at how witty and entertaining he can be. Jongin .. Kai always make me proud to be his fan. He’s the one that I can compliment without thinking that I need to do as duty. I really, genuinely like his works and don’t need to force myself or pretend that I like. There are many handsome and hot guys in the industry. There are also many other people who can sing and dance very well. But Jongin will always be my ultimate bias. The one that always has special place in my heart. Never once regret becoming your fan and I’ll always support you as much as I can. Thank you for always giving us high quality works like this. I love you.

author: @wilasineeu.6894
text: I started liking him for his visuals - handsome face, hot body, sexiness. I love him for his beautiful heart as a person. An artist who is much beloved from everyone that has worked with him. The one who cherishes his fans so much and always make us smile in every way possible. The one who always be kind and gentle and happy like a ball of sunshine. But what make me really stay as a fan even after years is his talent and passion. He always has that ‘wow factor’ that make me in awe and respect him. That talent that makes him stand out. And he even keeps growing and improving in all aspects. He’s always top-tier in dance, no doubt. But he also has beautiful voice and great taste in creating arts. He’s also growing as an entertainer who got people surprised at how witty and entertaining he can be. Jongin .. Kai always make me proud to be his fan. He’s the one that I can compliment without thinking that I need to do as duty. I really, genuinely like his works and don’t need to force myself or pretend that I like. There are many handsome and hot guys in the industry. There are also many other people who can sing and dance very well. But Jongin will always be my ultimate bias. The one that always has special place in my heart. Never once regret becoming your fan and I’ll always support you as much as I can. Thank you for always giving us high quality works like this. I love you.

text:
나도 모르게 제한하고 있었던 어떤 컨셉이라는 영역을 확장시켜주는 아티스트!
솔로 활동을 통해 좀 더 자신의 생각과 이야기를 표현해내고 또 그것을 온전히 감상하고 즐길 수 있는 카이의 팬이라는 것에 감사하다
아무도 시도하지 않았던 혹은 못했던 컨셉을 과감히 시도하면서도 자신의 뛰어난 능력으로 설득시키는 모습이 '이런 것도 표현할 수 있네? 이런 식으로도 표현이 가능하네?' 하며 매번 감탄하게 만든다
카이하면 퍼포먼스에만 집중이 되어있었는데 1집 앨범과 이번 Vanilla의 공개로 노래에 대한 기대감도 착실히 증폭시키는 중!

author: @reoney5126
text:
항상 예상을 뛰어넘어 허를 찌르는 무대와 퍼포먼스를 보여주는 최고의 아이돌. 엑소를 춤 잘추는 그룹으로 각인시킨 이 시대 최고의 센터. 아이돌 센터의 개념과 중요성을 다른 아이돌뿐 아니라 대중에게도 알린 엑소 카이가 이젠 그냥 카이라는 이름으로 브랜드화 된 느낌. 팬이 아니어도 전혀 모르는 사람이 봐도 저사람은 자기 색이 분명한 아티스트라는걸 보여주는 사람. 평장올림픽 폐회식 무대에서 아이돌팬이 아닌 일반인들이 근사한 댄서라고 생각하며 박수치며 무대를 보게 만든 사람. 갓카이 , 아이돌의 아이돌이라는 수식어에 그냥 수긍 할 수 밖에 없게 만드는 카이. 그 무엇보다도 노력이 결과물을 만든다는 평범한 진리를 무대로 보여주는 프로중의 프로. 
멋있어 참 멋지다. 이거 말고는 더 할 말이 없다. 너 참 멋지다

author: @1989kd
text:
I’m not a K-Pop follower, but this exudes such extraordinary artistry from the use of emotive colour palettes set against contrasting textures, especially the contrast of Kai’s dancing, like flowing water, which I always connect with freedom,  set against the roughness of stone, which is a beautiful metaphor for our complicated relationship with time. Perhaps I delve too deep but I love that his work stands alone against the rest of the industry and I mean that without offence: it is distinctly different and seems to do away with the following of trends to ensure that it is quite unique: it is not moulded from a place whereby the objective is to, say, break records. Clearly a lot of time and work goes into his projects and it is very telling. You know, it’s like visiting an art exhibition, one of my favourite places to go find myself.
*Excuse any grammatical errors*
🙂🙃

author: @mileidy_Towers
text:
Es increíble todo lo que JongIn puede transmitir. Aún recuerdo a esa persona tímida que se presentaba por primera vez como dancing machine de EXO y ahora que lo veo, después de años, sólo puedo decir que me llena de orgullo haber sido partícipe de su crecimiento. Hoy, al ver este video, me encuentro conmovida casi hasta las lágrimas, siento una gran calidez aunque sólo he estado tras una pantalla durante todo este tiempo. Estoy feliz y agradecida por haber conocido a EXO y a nuestro KAI. Sólo deseo que pueda continuar mostrando su talento y haciendo lo que más disfruta, incluso si es fuera de la empresa que no lo trata como se merece. Deseo que perciba todo el cariño que sentimos, aunque somos de países diferentes. Deseo que sea feliz. Deseo poder quedarme mucho tiempo y continuar apoyándole y disfrutar cada una de sus canciones. 
Démosle mucho apoyo a nuestro KAI que siempre da lo mejor de sí. Démosle mucho apoyo a nuestro JongIn que tanto se ha esforzado por demostrar que siempre puede superarse.

Он как будто строит свою персональную вселенную
Он не кто-то другой
Он как будто тот же Кай из эксо, который просто нам рассказывает свою историю
Все эти линии говорят о праработанности
Он не просто записал сольник, потому что хотел срубить кеш на имени

Чонин говорил, что он очень упорно трудился и это очень важно для него
Все правда
До последнего слова
 Потому что в противном случае так хорошо не получается
